Adam Patrick DeVine -LRB- born November 7 , 1983 -RRB- is an American actor , comedian , singer , screenwriter and producer .
He is a star and co-creator of the Comedy Central series Workaholics , as well as Adam DeVine 's House Party .
Since 2013 , he has portrayed Andy Bailey , the boyfriend of Haley Dunphy , on the critically acclaimed hit ABC sitcom Modern Family .
He has voiced main characters on animated series Uncle Grandpa and Penn Zero : Part-Time HeroHe played the role of Bumper Allen in the musical films Pitch Perfect and Pitch Perfect 2 .
His other film credits include the comedies Neighbors , The Intern , Ice Age : Collision Course , Mike and Dave Need Wedding Dates '' .